WHAT IS "COMMERCIAL USE"?

Commercial use includes, but is not limited to:

  × Selling the software or derivative works
  × Charging users to play or access the game
  × Displaying advertisements in or around the game
  × In-app purchases or premium features
  × Using in a product or service that generates revenue
  × Corporate training or team building (if charged for)
  × Any form of monetary gain or compensation

Acceptable non-commercial uses include:

  ✓ Personal hobby projects
  ✓ Educational purposes (schools, universities, tutorials)
  ✓ Non-profit organizations
  ✓ Open source contributions
  ✓ Research and study
  ✓ Free community projects

